  "description": {
    "lang": "eng",
    "value": "In lunary-ai/lunary version 1.5.6, the `/v1/evaluators/` endpoint lacks proper access control, allowing any user associated with a project to fetch all evaluator data regardless of their role. This vulnerability permits low-privilege users to access potentially sensitive evaluation data."
